            <description><![CDATA[<p>Release date: 2026-04-10</p>
<h2 id="improvements">Improvements</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Improved account and license syncing reliability.</strong>
NameQuick now uses an updated backend path for customer access and
license checks.</li>
<li><strong>Existing paid access restores more consistently.</strong>
Subscription state, customer lookups, and usage syncing now run through
the updated licensing flow.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="bug-fixes">Bug Fixes</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Improved security around billing and licensing
infrastructure.</strong> Sensitive billing credentials are now handled
entirely server-side.</li>
<li><strong>Updated release tooling for the new licensing flow.</strong>
Internal build and support scripts now align with the backend-managed
path.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
